flowchart TB
    Client([Client])
    Wallet[Wallet Service<br/>idempotency + validation]
    Orchestrator[Transfer Orchestrator<br/>same-shard ACID<br/>cross-shard TCC]
    ShardA[(Account Shard A<br/>transactional store)]
    ShardB[(Account Shard B<br/>transactional store)]
    EventLog[(Event Log<br/>partitioned stream)]
    Fraud[Fraud / Analytics<br/>async consumer]

    Client -->|transfer req| Wallet
    Wallet --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator <-->|ACID / TCC| ShardA
    Orchestrator <-->|ACID / TCC| ShardB
    ShardA -.->|emit entries| EventLog
    ShardB -.->|emit entries| EventLog
    EventLog -.->|consume| Fraud

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Wallet,Orchestrator,Fraud service
    class ShardA,ShardB,EventLog store
